OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773767470
OL,3,CChildren being 'failed by tech
OL,4,Ccompanies' amid rise in online sex
OL,5,Cabuse images
OL,7,FChild sex abuse image crimes logged by
OL,8,Fpolice forces in the UK have risen by
OL,9,Fnearly 10% in the past year, the
OL,10,Fchildren's charity NSPCC has said.
OL,12,FThe charity sent out Freedom of
OL,13,FInformation requests to UK police
OL,14,Fforces about crimes relating to
OL,15,Findecent and prohibited images of
OL,16,Fchildren, and its research found that
OL,17,Fthere were 36,829 such recorded cases
OL,18,Fbetween 1 April 2024 and 31 March 2025.
OL,20,FOf the 45 contacted, 42 police forces
OL,21,Fresponded to the NSPCC's request.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
