FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773767470
OL,3,CChildren being 'failed by tech
OL,4,Ccompanies' amid rise in online sex
OL,5,Cabuse images
OL,7,FA year-on-year comparison suggested
OL,8,Fthere was a 9% increase in recorded
OL,9,Foffences from 33,886 the year before,
OL,10,Fdata compiled by the charity found.
OL,12,FThe NSPCC, which aims to safeguard
OL,13,Fchildren against abuse, said the
OL,14,Ffindings have prompted renewed calls
OL,15,Ffor tech companies to block nude
OL,16,Fimages from being taken and shared on
OL,17,Fchildren's devices.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773767470
OL,3,CChildren being 'failed by tech
OL,4,Ccompanies' amid rise in online sex
OL,5,Cabuse images
OL,7,FIn December, the government's strategy
OL,8,Fto crack down on Violence Against
OL,9,FWomen and Girls (VAWG) said it aims to
OL,10,F"make it impossible for children in
OL,11,Fthe UK to take, share or view a nude
OL,12,Fimage," adding that it was "working
OL,13,Fconstructively with companies to make
OL,14,Fthis a reality".
OL,16,FHowever, the NSPCC has called for it
OL,17,Fto be made mandatory and urged the
OL,18,Fgovernment to do more to ensure tech
OL,19,Fcompanies are doing enough to block
OL,20,Fnude images from being created,
OL,21,Fshared, or viewed on children's phones.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773767470
OL,3,CChildren being 'failed by tech
OL,4,Ccompanies' amid rise in online sex
OL,5,Cabuse images
OL,7,FThe charity added that action should
OL,8,Fbe taken against those companies if
OL,9,Fthey fail to embed existing technology
OL,10,Fto protect children from seeing
OL,11,Findecent images online.
OL,13,FNSPCC chief executive Chris Sherwood
OL,14,Fsaid: "Children across the UK are
OL,15,Fbeing completely failed by tech
OL,16,Fcompanies that should be protecting
OL,17,Fthem online. We cannot keep letting
OL,18,Fthem off the hook when they can do
OL,19,Fmore to prevent this from happening in
OL,20,Fthe first place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773767470
OL,3,CChildren being 'failed by tech
OL,4,Ccompanies' amid rise in online sex
OL,5,Cabuse images
OL,7,F"Technology already exists that could
OL,8,Fbe deployed today to stop children
OL,9,Ffrom taking, sharing, or receiving
OL,10,Fnude images. So, the real question is:
OL,11,Fwhat's stopping them? If they continue
OL,12,Fto drag their feet, the government
OL,13,Fmust show its might by stepping in and
OL,14,Fcompelling them to act."
OL,16,FThe charity said that "device-level
OL,17,Fprotections" should be embedded by
OL,18,Fdefault to ensure children are granted
OL,19,Fautomatic protection, while adult
OL,20,Fusers would have the choice to opt out.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773767470
OL,3,CChildren being 'failed by tech
OL,4,Ccompanies' amid rise in online sex
OL,5,Cabuse images
OL,7,FThe technology can block a nude image
OL,8,Ffrom being taken, sent, or received on
OL,9,Fa device, which is a system the NSPCC
OL,10,Fsaid can enable abuse to be stopped at
OL,11,Fthe source and prevent indecent images
OL,12,Ffrom ever being created or sent.
OL,14,FHowever, the use of end-to-end
OL,15,Fencryption, a secure communication
OL,16,Fprocess where only the sender and
OL,17,Fintended recipient can read the
OL,18,Fmessages, on social media platforms
OL,19,Fcould be hiding the true scale of
OL,20,Fabuse children experience online.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773767470
OL,3,CChildren being 'failed by tech
OL,4,Ccompanies' amid rise in online sex
OL,5,Cabuse images
OL,7,FThe NSPCC said that of the 10,811
OL,8,Fcrimes where police forces recorded
OL,9,Fwhich social media platforms
OL,10,Fperpetrators used in relation to child
OL,11,Fsex abuse image crimes, 43%, or a
OL,12,Ftotal of 4,615, took place on Snapchat.
OL,14,FMeanwhile, Meta, which owns Facebook,
OL,15,FInstagram, and WhatsApp accounted for
OL,16,Falmost a quarter of all offences
OL,17,F(24%), the charity said.
OL,19,FSafeguarding minister, Jess Phillips,
OL,20,Fsaid the data uncovered by the NSPCC
OL,21,Fwas "nothing short of deeply shocking".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
