CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773767470
OL,3,CChildren being 'failed by tech
OL,4,Ccompanies' amid rise in online sex
OL,5,Cabuse images
OL,7,F"We have committed to making it
OL,8,Fimpossible for children in the UK to
OL,9,Ftake, share or view nude images, and
OL,10,Fhave already announced a ban on
OL,11,Fsocalled 'nudification' apps to stop
OL,12,Fabusive images being created and
OL,13,Fspread in the first place.
OL,15,F"We will not hesitate to go further
OL,16,Funtil our children are safe from
OL,17,Fsexual abuse online."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
