SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773767470
OL,3,CChildren being 'failed by tech
OL,4,Ccompanies' amid rise in online sex
OL,5,Cabuse images
OL,7,FEarlier this month, it was announced
OL,8,Fthat nudification apps - applications
OL,9,Fand websites that produce deepfake
OL,10,Fnude images of real people using
OL,11,Fgenerative AI - would be criminalised
OL,12,Fas part of the Crime and Police Bill,
OL,13,Fwhich is currently going through
OL,14,FParliament.
OL,16,FCurrently, social media regulations in
OL,17,Fthe UK restrict children under the age
OL,18,Fof 13 from having social media.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
