PN,31411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1773767470
OL,3,CChildren being 'failed by tech
OL,4,Ccompanies' amid rise in online sex
OL,5,Cabuse images
OL,7,FCompanies like Snapchat, Instagram,
OL,8,FFacebook, and TikTok say they have
OL,9,Fmeasures in place to verify the age of
OL,10,Fchildren, as well as ways to restrict
OL,11,Ftheir access to harmful content.
OL,13,FCommunications regulator Ofcom has
OL,14,Fwritten to Facebook, Instagram,
OL,15,FSnapchat, and others, giving them
OL,16,Funtil the end of April to explain what
OL,17,Factions they are taking on age checks
OL,18,Fand grooming protections.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
